data.title: Category:Irina Pavlovna Paley
data.text:
Princess Irina Pavlovna Paley, (December 21, 1903 – November 15, 1990), was the daughter of Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich of Russia and his second wife, Olga Valerianovna Paley.

<nowiki>Irene Románova; Irina Pavlovna Palej; Ирина Палей; Irina Pawlowna Paley; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Ірына Паўлаўна Палей; 伊琳娜·巴甫洛夫娜·帕雷; Irina Palej; Irina Pavlovna Paley; イリナ・パーレイ; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Ιρίνα Πάλεϊ; ايرينا بالى; Irina Palej; Ірина Павлівна Палій; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Irina Paley; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Princess Irina Pavlovna Paley; An Banphrionsa Irina Pavlovna Paley; Irina Pavlovna Romanovová; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Princesa Paléi; orosz nemes; aristócrata francesa (1903–1990); noble russe, exilée après la révolution; κόρη του Μεγάλου Δούκα Παύλου Αλεξάντροβιτς της Ρωσίας; russische Adelige, Enkelin von Zar Alexander II.; aristocrate uit Keizerrijk Rusland (1903-1990); daughter of Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich of Russia; principessa Romanovskaja; ruská princezna; French siyaasa nira ŋun nyɛ paɣa; Ирина Павловна Палей; Палей, Ирина Павловна; イリナ・パーリィ; イリーナ; Irina Pavlovna Palei; Irina Pavlovna Paley; Irina Pavlovna Palej; Irina Pavlovna Palej; Irene Romanova</nowiki>
